message.entry: SigmaGaussian1 must be a strictly positive finite scalar real number.
SigmaGaussian2 must be a strictly positive finite scalar real number.
CenterFreqGaussian1 must be a scalar real number between -1 and 1.
CenterFreqGaussian2 must be a scalar real number between -1 and 1.
GainGaussian1 must be a non-negative finite scalar real number.
GainGaussian2 must be a non-negative finite scalar real number.
GainGaussian1 and GainGaussian2 cannot both be zero.
